Kepa: Kepa no es un monstruo fuerte. Sin embargo, atacarlo sin cuidado podría hacerte llorar.
Existen personas que a veces intentan comer Kepas Grandes. No los dejes.
Contrario a la creencia popular, los Kepas Rojos son los que más se parecen al Kepa original.
A pesar de su dura piel, el Hamming es un monstruo muy débil.
Originalmente tallos de una planta, el Chinency desde entonces ha evolucionado a su forma actual.
Se sabe muy poco acerca de la estructura interna del Jukopus.
Dependiendo de su madurez, Este monstruo puede desarrollar diversas técnicas de combate.
Hay muchas cosas que debes saber sobre este monstruo. Sobre todo, no te dejes golpear por su embestida.
Incluso luego de mutar, su carne es aún comestible.
Las almas de aquellos que se aventuraron al inframundo ahora aparecen como demonios.
Un alma que no recibió la guía de la Diosa. Fue engendrado a través de control demoníaco.
Rondando entre las sombras del bosque, éste monstruo ha evolucionado su tamaño a lo largo del tiempo.
Éste monstruo creció, pero no ha cambiado mucho. Incluso en el pasado, solía ser una planta despiadada y letal.
Se desconoce si los Vubbes luchadores son entrenados o tienen una aptitud natural para el combate.
Algunos dicen que una Meduja puede ser usada para contactar con las almas de los muertos.
Investigadores han afirmado que las plantas tienen alma. Las Meduja son la forma mutada de esas almas.
Hay gente que preferiría recibir una flecha al mordisco de un Bite.
Es un secreto olvidado que los demonionos desplegaron a los Puragis en secreto para atacar a los soldados de Ruklys durante la guerra cívil.
Los Puragis Azules aman matar y saquear.
Jamás nadie ha visto la cara oculta tras su máscara.
Estos secuaces demoníacos disfrutan las matanzas.
Un secuaz demoníaco encontrado alrededor del mundo.
La razón por la cual los Pescadores son considerados monstruos se debe a que sus cañas controlan a las criaturas.
Las acciones de éste pescador son a veces inexplicables.
El vástago en su cabeza puede ser usado para diversos propósitos, cómo cebo atrayante y detector de blancos ocultos.
Si el Matsum se origino de una planta, animal o mineral no es relevante. Lo que debes saber es que es peligroso.
A pesar de que sus colores los hacen muy llamativos, es muy difícil esquivar sus ataques.
Este monstruo ha sido descrito como duro de bloquear y duro de comer.
Un monstruo grande, fuerte y duro, raramente presa de cazadores.
Los Kepas envejecen rápidamente a cambio de su fuerza. Ten cuidado con su caústico olor, que se ha vuelto más fuerte con la edad.
Su arruinado color por envejecer sólo reafirma su peligrosidad.
Las hojas de esta planta son más fuertes que el cuero.
Incluso luego de sufrir mutaciones, los Raffly continúan cazando pequeños insectos.
Aunque mutó de una hierba, ahora todo su cuerpo está hecho de sólida madera.
Atacar sus piernas no causará que se derrumbe.
Los fantasmas afectados por demonios a menudo cambian su apariencia de esta manera.
A diferencia de otros monstruos espectrales, estos monstruos eran almas malvadas incluso cuando estaban vivos.
Esta semilla flotante fue transmutada perdiendo su suavidad exterior por un cuesco sólido y espinoso. Sin embargo, su flotabilidad se mantuvo intacta.
El hecho que los hombres de madera no puedan moverse es una bendición.
Aunque los Limos son muy similares, sus especies varían en base a los materiales de los cuales se originaron.

Estos guardianes fueron emplazados en varios lugares, empezando con el Mausoleo Real de Zachariel el Grande, para detener a los invasores. Su nombre proviene de los saqueadores de tumbas que se han encontrado con ellos.
Los Madakias fueron creados por magos de la corte para expulsar intrusos más peligrosos que los saqueadores de tumbas.
El Rodador es una de las diversas creaciones mágicas hechas para proteger tumbas selladas sin un guardian.
La caballería de roca del Mausoleo Real es una creación mágica diseñada para hacerle frente incluso al más armado de los caballeros.
Por razones desconocidas, este monstruo le tiene un odio sin par a los humanos. Prefiere atacar humanos a otra presa más apropiada, incluso a costa de su propia supervivencia.
Las hojas que se caen del cadáver de un Hanaming se marchitan rápidamente.
Sus números aumentaron luego del Gran Cataclismo Silvano; ahora tienden a competir con los humanos por territorio.
Los Chupacabras se mueven de manera muy sigilosa. Con eso dicho, es mucho más peligroso para los humanos si se trata de Chupacabras élite.
Se dice que el canto de un Popoleón puede romper vidrio.
La Tontulia es una mutación más móvil del Tontus.
Cuando los cactús mutaron en Tontus la vida de los habitantes del desierto empeoró.
Comparado con otra especies animales, El Vekarabe no cambió mucho cuando se conviritó en monstruo. Sin embargo, su agresividad es definitivamente nueva.
El nombre de este monstruo se adecúa a su apariencia, pero no refleja del todo su naturaleza.
El Boowook es uno de los muchos sistemas defensivos dejados por Zachariel el Grande en el Mausoleo Real.
Pino fue nombrado así por sus primeros descubridores, tras notar que guardaba relación con Geppetto.
Monstruos que simplemente aumentaron su tamaño y agresividad son un placer a la vista, al menos cuando se comparan con los otros terrores sobre este mundo.
Aunque este monstruo no es particularmente hostíl contra los humanos, ataca a cualquier animal de sangre caliente.
Aunque originalmente fue creado para defender el Mausoleo Real, desde ese entonces ha cambiado a un estado en el que ataca a cualquiera que entre.
Aunque que la Cocatriz es muy pequeña, su terrible aliento y mirada puede petrificar a sus enemigos al instante.
Aunque su apariencia puede ser confundida con otros monstruos similares, los Zinutekas fueron construídos artificialmente con magia.
A pesar de su apariencia, el Pokubu puede ser muy feroz.
Lo que es más aterrador que el suave y queratinizado pelo de una Dandel, es su vitalidad y agresividad.
Debido al ambiente, este monstruo adopta una variedad de formas. Éste evolucionó para tener alas.
A pesar de su apariencia, estas criaturas no están huecas por dentro.
Originalmente fue creado con buenas intenciones, pero ahora el Golem vive poseído por una energía malvada.
Un demonio menor invocado por sus superiores para invadir las torres.
Hay incontables tipos de estos demonios menores debido a su gran número.
Alguna vez esta especie fue rara; sin embargo, sus numeros han aumentado significativamente.
la Cocatriz Enorme es muy peligrosa, su mriada y aliento petrifican al enemigo. Enfrentar a esta criatura no debe ser tomado a la lígera.
El número de Gusanos Saco no ha ido en aumento, aunque con su población actual la extinción no es un problema.
Su cuerpo se desvanece si te alejas por el tiempo suficiente.
Usó su gancho para aferrarse a un monstruo de mayor tamaño y así escapar del reino demoníaco; cambió mucho en el proceso.
Aunque ahora se leña menos, los monstruos originados por tocones siguen apareciendo. Aparentemente se forman de residuos de monstruos tipo planta.
Golem de Grava de las Catacumbas
Bomba de Tiempo (sólo para puntuar en mazmorra)
(Temporal) Dispositivo de Control de la Prision
Una teoría popular indica que debes ser un demonio para poder usar este mensajero.
El Vubbe más común de encontrar.
A lo largo del tiempo, los Vubbes se han vuelto diversos e indistinguibles.
Es difícil determinar si sus roles mineros son permanentes debido a que se sabe muy poco del sistema social de los Vubbes.
Los Arqueros Vubbe se especializan en usar armas de rango. Además hay personas que aseguran que los Vubbes tienen roles definidos.
Es posible recolectar y usar los arcos y flechas que los Vubbes hacen.
Un arbusto monstruoso que ataca lanzando ramas o golpeando con ellas.
De acuerdo a la legende este perro guardían es una creación que Zachariel el grande había planeado preservar.
Debido a su linda apariencia muchos han tratado de conquistar el corazon de Tini, ninguno lo ha logrado.
El Árbol Ambulo es diferente a muchos monstruos originados en el reino demoníaco pues no es una deformación de un ser o cosa.
Está muy bien entrenado para obedecer todas las órdenes de su amo. Lamentablemente, su dueño usualmente es un demonio.
Los Despojos son unos monstruos tipo demonio originados cómo un sub-producto de cuando un monstruo más poderoso es transformado en fantasma.
El Yekub desata su infame grito que produce millares de secuaces. Yekubite es el nombre dado a esos secuaces.
Un monstruo poseído que está obsesionado con las divinas Estatuas de la Diosa.
Este monstruo no parece haber sido transmutado de plantas sino que de flora podrida. Sin embargo, no hay evidencia que apoye esta conclusión.
Luego de transformarse en un monstruo con un cuerpo de madera reforzado y sin hojas, el Árbgool ha reemplazado su dieta fotosíntetica con la caza.
Desde tiempos inmemoriales, Ammon ha dañado incontables personas y monstruos.
Aunque mantuvo su forma original, el Operador ha desarrollado un comportamiento extremedamente violento y peligroso.
Un híbrido entre Avispa y Escarabajo gravemente mutado que comparte carácteristicas de ambos, operan en enjambres.
Antes de que fuese revelada cómo una planta, se especulaba que era la larva de un monstruo.
Los animales que vivían en el Mausoleo Real han sido deformados por la energía maligna.
Es una criatura mágica cuyo nombre proviene de los deseos de los golems.
Una criatura mágica creada para proteger el Mausoleo Real. A pesar de ser débil, es lo suficientemente fuerte cómo para resistir los poderes de las Diosas.
A pesar de su apariciencia, esta creación mágica ha recibido la bendición de la Diosa. Puede causarle daño crítico a los Demonios.
Muchas criaturas fueron colocadas en el Mausoleo Real, incluyendo el Undetumbas, para protegerlo contra los demonios.
Los rumores dicen que la Tejedora se encuentra buscando telas de roca.
Firm and toxic, their blood-sucking ability is unique.
A diferencia de los Golems tradicionales; el Zolem es movido por un aura misteriosa, no magia.
Aunque es un Kepa de nombre, realmente provino del reino demoniaco.
Un goblin malvado, invocado por los Vubbes. A veces aparece en áreas donde no hay signos de Vubbes.
Monstruo mutante que se ve cómo un delfín. Sus otras características corresponden a una Ballena de Piedra pequeña.
Aunque es un tipo de Clyra por su cola, est monstruo parece haber sido transmutado de una calabaza.
A medida que la población de demonios se expandió, nuevas especies aparecieron. El Infrortador es una de esas especies.
En el pasado este animal era muy amigable con los humanos pero ahora es más peligroso que un oso.
Los Armaduri son dullahans cuya armadura es mantenida por energía maligna.
Un demonio que respeta al fuerte y es cruel contra el débil. Aunque, su agresividad vuelve trivial esta característica.
No se sabe con certeza a que monstruo se parece el Infroburk, pero ciertamente es feroz.
Ellos matan a sus camaradas demoníacos por ocio.
Un pequeño monstruo que es mitad tortuga, mitad mineral. Prefiere vivir solo que en grupo.
Debido a su apariencia, los mineros novatos tratan de extraer sus espaldas y son atacados.
Aquellos que ven al Filipo cómo un ser pequeño y adorable son rápidamente atacados por él.
Actúan cómo secuaces exploradores de Mirtis, estos murciélagos solían vivir en todo el mundo, pero se han convertido en una amenaza mayor a pesar de su reducido tamaño.
Although the Hogmas are smarter than the Vubbes and can use tools, their brutish instincts stifle any progress and lead to many stupid mistakes.
Levelheaded Hogmas are often seen taking the role of Arqueros.
Some Hogmas have picked up abilities through experience but they still have Hogma instincts.
It is said that they receive their powers from human souls because they gather toward the injured.
This type of Ellom is toxic.
Merog variant. Slight differences in the mutation process differentiates the variety of Merogs.
This reptile monstruo attacks instinctively but shows as much abilities as its intelligence.
A Hogma whose intelligence and instinct give them leadership in the fight against humans.
A monstruo which is said to be created by demons using the Chupacabra.
It is both filthy in nature and surly in its appearance.
It is fierce against other monstruos and humans, more so especially with Insect-type monstruos.
Amphibians that have branched out and evolved to be able to hunt in arid areas, travelers should be wary of them.
A monstruo with a habit of baiting and attacking humans.
You can tell the origin of this beast just by its name or appearance.
Tama is a monstruo originating from the spores of some plants. It is unclear whether it will still grow from its current form.
Kepari are not related with the Kepa, and are instead akin to animals.
Since the disappearance of the Diosas, one of the most bizarre change is that these water-dwelling creatures are now active on land.
It still tends to gravitate toward rotten flesh.
Skill Point Up Estatua de Diosa
It is not yet clear what deforms into this monstruo.
Similar to the Lemur, but cold-resistant.
While they look like guardsmen, these Hogmas have extensive battle experience.
Compared to an average Hogmas, they are very stronger, but their intelligence is lower.
It is a monstruo that is formed by binding an animal with a mineral. In recent years, various forms of these monstruos have been discovered.
It is one of several variations of Zinute.
A variety of Chupacabra dwell in various places, causing harm to both human life and crops.
Although small, it has grown bigger than its original state and hunts for meat throughout its life
While it has no eyes, Arma has a highly developed sense of hearing and smell.
It attacks people with a flame ball that it cherishes and carries around.
A monstruo variant that comes from a wizard's belongings. It is resistive to its original use.
A sad monstruo that can't fly.
While it was once a creature created by a wizard using the best magic available, it has now turned hostile to humans due to the influence of the demons.
When the demons captured the Torre del Mago, this doll was greatly affected. In particular, it instinctively hates magic users.
The slime is an organism in the demon realm. Its population exploded after the time when the plant Geant, especially around the Torre del Mago.
One of the demon's lower level creature.They possess a little bit of intelligence.
When botanists first discovered the Raflorecia, they planned on naming it Tripede, a name that has since been given to another monstruo.
A monstruo whose habitat has been relocated close to the volcano.
A hybrid monstruo that exhibit the advantages of having the body of two known beasts.
Ultanuns have always been flightless birds even before its deformation.
Don't let its cute appearance fool you. This monstruo will try to tear you apart, given the chance.
A Panto variant with distinctively high intelligence. They often show up with the other Panto variants.
The Panto Cháman is powerful, but it does not know were they are in a developing type of wizard. The obvious point is that you must pay more attention to them during combat.
A somewhat cute mutant that is always expressionless. They assemble together when chanting.
Moyabu has evolved from the Moya. It is more violent than the Moya.
When it comes to flight, Bavon would be better just floating there as is.
A carnivorous plant that uses bait to catch food. It shred its food into pieces before swallowing.
A three headed monstruo. It is hard to tell whether the main body is just one head or all three.
This beast that once exclusively roamed in the demon realm. Nowadías it is found all over the world, endangering other wildlife and humans.
The demons have tamed Denden and uses it for their means.
If a moving poisonous mushroom makes you anxious, consider Doyor as an example.
The yellow grass on its body looks supple. But if you touch it, it can be quite painful .
The Rondo is not an animal found in our world, rather it is an animal that crossed from the demon realm.
The Terra Imp is quite mischievous. One should be aware of their belongings, as they might steal them.
Although it appears to have no sharp edges, it will when engaged in battle.
There are not too many cases of a fruit deformed monstruos. Leafnut belongs to these few cases.
Its elongated pupils are a distinctive feature.
A Panto with excellent fighting skills and is one of the strongest subspecies in the forest.
The flowers around its neck are actually real flowers rather than decorations.
If you carelessly touch the leaves on its head, Mali will unleash its relentless anger towards you.
Be aware of the smoke that this creature spurts as it is highly toxic and will last for a while.
A bite from its sharp beak causes persistent pain, which may last for a while.
The edges of its wings are covered in poison. Touching it may cause paralysis.
A low-ranking demon who is always looking for opportunities to promote itself.
The Seedmia are very troublesome as they are able to shoot seeds over exceptionally long distances.
A moving tree monstruo that appeared after the Great Plant Cataclysm, it was named after its discoverer.
Galok is a monstruo who command workers in the demon realm.
Upent rapidly appeared from what once were flora with magical powers.
When the demons found Glagartons, they immediately subjugated them into minions. Glagartons that aren't minions are still dangerous to humans.
The Corylus is a mutant hybrid between plants, animals and minerals.
The reduction in size isn't the only thing that got better after this beast mutated.
It is simple and effective for Beeteros to camouflage. Please do not touch the swaying leaf as it can stab you.
A mutated mantis. It has gotten stronger and has developed the ability to camouflage.
Egnomes carry a stern look. The more stern it looks, the more powerful it is.
After mutating, Beetow has developed an unreasonable and venomous nature. Its aggression has also become more significant.
Sister of Pawnd. It carries a sickle larger than its own body.
Carcashu is a fungus. Its toxins are strong, but there are parts of it that can be eaten.
The Maíz Negro looks deceptively delicious, eating one will certainly poison you.
This monstruo was bred by the demons and is known for its poisonous abilities.
Please don't assume that Lapasape can only be encountered in the deep forest, as it sometimes prowl outside to eat human crops.
Its appearance did not change much, but its physicality has. Lives near water.
This monstruo was once the size of a little finger, but it has since grown greatly.
This monstruo has evolved from a bird and has since lost its ability to fly.
The Dumaro is a newly discovered monstruo, which developed its toxic abilities after the Great Plant Cataclysm.
The Lichenclops doesn't only have good eye sight, their sense of smell is also exceptional.
Infroblood is a case where plant spores transform into monstruos. It can float.
Ticen wanders around with a spear, it tends to group with other Ticen variants.
A tip of Tucen's tail is made out of minerals.
Since it retains its memory before deformation, this monstruo has grudges against the people who felled it.
Although this monstruo looks small, it has already reached its adulthood. So it might only grow just a bit more.
The Woodfung is closely related to witchcraft.
They exhibit a unique hull that is a mix between stone and iron.
Estatua de la Diosa Zemyna D
Estatua de la Diosa Zemyna E
Estatua de la Diosa Vakarine D
Estatua de la Diosa Vakarine E
It is speculated whether this underground spirit has been deformed and corrupted.
It has been said that Helgasercle was made by the servants of the demon realm's aristocrats.
Ruta de la Penitencia of Great Catedral

PS/PM/Resistencia consumidos pueden ser recuperados a través de alas siguientes opciones.
La Recuperación Espontánea es más lenta comparada a otros métodos, pero no requiere que el personaje haga algo.
[Recuperación por Pociones]: Recupera PS/PM/Resistencia inmediatamente usando pociones.
Las pociones tienen un tiempo de enfriamiento antes de volver a ser empleadas.
[Raíz Cristal del Árbol]: Destruye Raíces Cristal del Árbol para recuperar Resistencia.
{memo }Las Raíces Cristal del Árbol aparecen aleatoriamente en los campos.
[Modo Descanso]: Prender una fogata durante el Modo Descanso acelera tu recuperación.
La recuperación durante el Modo Descanso es más rápida que la Recuperación Espontánea, y es inclusive más valoz si prendes una fogata durante el Modo Descanso.
Exterminio se activará si matas al monstruo con un golpe final muy fuerte.
Exterminio será activado si le haces más daño al monstruo que sus PS restantes con un ataque poderoso.
Destruir una Raíz Cristal del Árbol recupera tu Resistencia.
Hay muchas Raíces Cristal del Árbol en cada campo.
La Resistencia de todos los personajes a tu alrededor será recuperada si destruyes Raíces Cristal del Árbol.
Algunas habilidades se pueden sobrecalentar cuando se usan un cierto número de veces.
Si se activa el sobrecalentamiento, esa habilidad entra en enfriamiento y serás incapaz de usarla por un tiempo.
El Sobrecalentamiento será activado si el indicador de la habilidad se llena.
Para evitar el sobrecalentamiento de una habilidad, puedes alternar su uso con ataques normales.
El sobrecalentamiento puede ser suprimido usando otras habilidades.
Una vez sobrecalentada, no serás capaz de usar la Habilidad afectada.
El número de veces que has usado una Habilidad se reinicia al pasar el tiempo.

Los Espadachínes son guerreros con una gran fuerza física.{nl}Usan varias armas para enfrentar a los enemigos de cerca{nl}y ser la primera línea.
Los Highlanders son fieros guerreros que usan espadas de dos manos. Hacen que sus enemigos se estrellen contra si mismos o contra el terreno, así que son perfectos para enfrentarse a varios enemigos.
Los Peltasta son guerreros defensivos que usan sus escudos para bloquear y provocar a los enemigos.
Los Hoplitas usan lanzas con un gran rango de ataque. Obtienen bonificaciones cuando luchan contra enemigos fuertes y de gran tamaño.
Los Centuriones dirigen la batalla con formaciones. Controlan a sus aliados y usan distintas formaciones dependiendo de la situación.
Los Bárbaros son guerreros temerarios y agresivos que no se apegan a las reglas del combate y harán cualquier cosa para conseguir la victoria.
Los Catafractos usan lanzas de dos manos. Actúan cómo una caballería para abrirse paso y romper las filas enemigas.
Los Rodeleros emboscan y demuelen a sus enemigos. Sus habilidades defensivas con escudos son útiles para repeler ataques de rango.
Los Magos usan la magia para atacar y protegerse a si mismos.{nl}Pueden realizar Hechizos poderosos y concentrados,{nl} caúsandole daño a sólo un blanco o a múltiples blancos en un área.
Los Piromantes usan sucesivos golpes de magia de fuego para lucahr contra múltiples enemigos.
Los Criomantes usan poderosa magia de hielo para congelar a sus enemigos, o para proteger a sus aliados usando murallas de hielo.
Los Mentalistas usan la psicoquinesis para controlar la gravedad, o atraer enemigos y lanzarlos.
Hechiceros invocan y controlan espíritus para atacar a sus enemigos o inclusive usarlos cómo montura.
Los Vinculadores unen a los aliados para reducir el daño que reciben o conectan a sus enemigos para magnificar el daño que les inflingen.
Los Nigromantes son magos que emplean magia relacionada a la muerte. Atacan o crean invocacaciones usando los cadáveres que van recolectando.
Los Taumaturgos usan magia que cambia los atributos y tamaños de sus blancos. Pueden empequeñecer a sus enemigos o fortalecer a sus aliados para ayudarlos en combate.

Los Elementalistas dominan los elementos y pueden conjurar poderosos ataques mágicos. Sin embargo sus hechizos tienen un gran tiempo de enfriamiento, así que se recomienda cooperar con otros jugadores.
Los Arqueros usan arcos y un variado equipo secundario.{nl}Su especialidad son ataques ágiles y a distancia.

Los Cazadores son entrenadores que cazan a sus enemigos con sus compañeros. Los Compañeros usan habilidades que requieren la cooperación de sus dueños, cómo morder y retener a los enemigos, o encontrando blancos ocultos.
Los Ballesteros usan una Ballesta y un escudo para el combate estratégico. Pueden defenderse de ataques de rango emplazando un Pavés en la tierra.
Los Guardabosques se especializan en luchar contra múltiples enemigos con sus ataques rápidos y de rango.
Los Zapadores son arqueros que cosntruyen trampas y atraen a los enemigos a ellas.
Un Wugushi se especializa en usar varios tipos de veneno para atacar o confundir a sus enemigos.
Los Exploradores se especializan en reconocimiento e infiltración. Usan el sigilo para esconderse y transmitir la situación de los enemigos a sus aliados, entregando una ventaja táctica.
Los Clérigos curan y protegen a sus alíados a través de las benciones de la Diosa, mientras se deshacen de sus enemigos con poderosos golpes.
Los Sacerdotes son clérigos que dan bendiciones y resucitan a los muertos con sus poderes sagrados.
Los Krivis son sacerdotes que usan un fuego divino para ayudar a sus aliados o causar daño masivo a los enemigos.
Los Bokors usan habilidades vudú para levantar a los muertos o maldecir a sus enemigos para atacarlos a distancia.
Un Sadhu puede usar su alma para atacar a los enemigos con ataques imprevisibles o dar sus poderes a sus alíados.
Un Escultor Santo puede esculpir y emplazar estatuas sagradas. Sus estatuas pueden proteger a sus alíados o atacar enemigos.
Los Monjes son clérigos que se entrenan en la artes marciales a través de la bendición de la Diosa.
Los Redentores son clérigos que no sienten verguenza en aumentar su riqueza a través de la bendición de la Diosa.
Los Paladínes usan su poder sagrado para proteger a los alíados y desvanecer enemigos a través de las bendiciones de la Diosa.

The 7mo bishop of the Ignatius Catedral closed the Catedral after the appearance of ghosts, and now resides in Klaipeda.

The girl in charge of the mercenary guild's request desk. {nl}Attacked by monstruos during escape, she was saved by the captain of the mercenary guild.{nl}She soon joined the mercenaries and is now a proud mercenary herself.

The First Bishop of the St. Ignatius Catedral, he reformed the church himself by cleansing its false past.{nl}After his death, he continues to be remembered, with the St. Ignatius Catedral bearing his name.

As the Diosa who brings the break of dawn, she is called many names.{nl}The Diosa of Dawn. The Daughter of God. The representative of all Diosas.{nl}Carrying out the divine will, she looked after a tree. After she was kidnapped by the Demon Gods, the tree lost control and devoured the capital of the human world.

The Diosa of Fate. She can see a thousand years into the future, and prepare accordingly to alter the course of destiny.{nl}She left the Reveladores a revelation every 100 years. It is said collecting all the scattered revelations will grant one the power to confront fate.

Highlanders are tough fighters who use two-handed swords. They make enemies collide against each other or against terrain, so they are great for handling multiple enemies.
Centurions command the battle with formations. They control their allies and use different formations depending on the situation.
Corsairs are specialized in dual-wielding and ambushing enemies from behind. Anyone who joins a Corsario's party becomes a pirate.
Mercenarios are mercenaries who endure high risk for high rewards. They dangerously expose themselves to enemies to receive high attack power or high EXP.
Squires are warriors who support their allies. They support by repairing and enhancing others' weapons, or by setting up a base camp to aid their team.
Alquimistas use alchemy to enhance gems and synthesize or craft items.
Hechiceros summon and control spirits to fight enemies, or even to use as mounts.
Cronomantes are wizards who control time. They stop, speed up, or change back time to help allies.
Nigromantes are wizards who utilize magic involving the dead. They attack with, or create summoned creatures, using corpses collected over time.
Rogues are combat professionals who will do anything for victory. They're specialized at ambushing enemies from behind using bows and daggers.
Schwarzer Reiters maneuver quickly. They specialize in diverse shooting techniques using a pistol.
Flecheros make and use special arrows. Different arrows result in powerful attacks depending on the type of enemy and combat situation.
Halconeros control Hawks. Hawks may be fussy, but they become reliable companions when trained well.
Druídas are Clérigos who use the power of nature. They control plants to help allies, or transform into monstruos to use that monstruo's abilities.
Oráculos are Clérigos who possess foresight. They can predict or interfere with an enemy's attacks and determine their fate.

FAQ : Guarida{nl}1) Puedes cambiar el nombre de tu Guarida dandole click a 'Configuración de Guarida'. {nl}2) Puedes comprar aspectos para tu Guarida usando TP al darle click a 'Cambiar Guarida'.{nl}3) Puedes elegir el canal al que deseas ingresar desde tu Guarida.

FAQ : Character PS, PM, RES {nl}1) You can check your character's information on the upper left side of the screen. {nl}2) RES: This is stamina. When your RES is 0, you can only walk and cannot run anymore. {nl} RES is also used when learning certain attributes. {nl} RES can be recovered by destroying Raíces Cristal del Árbol or by using Resistencia Pills. {nl} Resistencia Pills can be purchased from shops, earned by completing quests or by defeating boss monstruos.

FAQ : Character Level & Class Level{nl}1) You can check the info at the lower part of your screen. {nl}2) Character Level: this is the level of your character. {nl}3) Class Level: this is the level of the class you chose. {nl} You can advance to another class when your Class Level has reached 15.

FAQ : Quick Slot{nl}1) You can add items and skills to the quick slot at the lower part of your screen. {nl}2) Skills are automatically added to the quick slot when you learn them. {nl}3) You can use up to 40 quick slots. {nl}4) Quick slots can be locked or unlocked. {nl}You cannot add or remove items or skills in the quick slot when it is locked.
FAQ : Changing Channels{nl}1) You can change channels by clicking on the channel button above the minimap. {nl}2) You can change channels in the Guarida before entering the world.

FAQ : Modo Descanso{nl}1) Press the INSERT key to switch to Modo Descanso. {nl}2) PS, PM, RES will be restored. {nl}3) You can light up a bonfire, craft items, enhance gems or combine cards in Modo Descanso.{nl} You need 'Firewood' to create a bonfire. {nl} PS, PM, RES is restored quicker when you use a bonfire.{nl}4) Other functions will be added in the near future.

FAQ : Durability & Potential{nl}1) Durability : Decreases a little bit when you play with the equipment on.{nl}    When an item's durability decreases below a certain level, the item's icon will be displayed on the right side of the quick slot.{nl}   When the durability completely diminishes, you won't benefit from the effects of your equipment.{nl}2) Potential : Decreases when you trade or enhance an equipment. The item with its Potential all depleted can't be traded or enhanced.

FAQ : Enhancement{nl}1) Weapons and armors can be enhanced using the anvil item. {nl}2) You can buy anvils from the Mercader de Objetos in any town. {nl}3) Plata is required for enhancing items.{nl}4) The enhancement of weapons and armor have a 100% success rate till +5 and +3 respectively. The chance of failure after the next enhancement will increase.{nl} If an enhancement fails, your enhancement level will reset and the Potential of your item decreases.

FAQ : Attributes{nl}1) There are attributes that you can learn from the class specific Masters. {nl}2) You can learn different types of attributes depending on what class you are. {nl} If you advance to a Montaraz, you can learn the 'Use Two-handed Swords' attribute from the Montaraz Master and use two-handed swords. {nl}3) Masters who teach attributes are located all around the map.
FAQ : Charge Skills{nl}1) Charge Skills are triggered only when you press down the quick slot button of the skill. {nl}2) A Charge Skill is canceled when you are attacked while using it.
FAQ : System Menu{nl}1) You can change to 'Controller UI Mode' through game settings when you are using a controller. {nl}2) There is a special 'Low Mode' for PCs with minimum system requirements.

FAQ : Chatting{nl}1) Shout: Enter '/y' before your message to show your message to all the players in the game. {nl} It requires a Megaphone item to do so. {nl}2) Party Chat: Enter '/p' before your message to chat with the party members in your party. {nl}Whisper: Enter '/w Team Name' before your message to talk privately with the player of that Team Name.

FAQ : Inventory Weight{nl}1) Shows the weight of the items you can carry. {nl}2) Weight increases by 5 when you increase your CON stat after a level up. {nl}3) Your character will walk regardless of RES when you're overencumbered.

FAQ : Minimap, Zone Map, World Map{nl}1) Click on the +, - buttons on the minimap to zoom in and zoom out. {nl}2) Click on the M button on the minimap or press the M key to view the full map of the zone (Zone Map) you are in. {nl}3) Press the N key on your keyboard to view the entire World Map.

Methods to restore your consumed PS/PM/Resistencia.
While you are in Modo Descanso, it is possible to light a [Bonfire] to speed up your recovery.
[Bonfire]: While in Modo Descanso, light a Bonfire to speed up your recovery.
{memo }Natural Recovery is very slow compared to other methods, but does not have any requirements.
{memo }{nl}{nl}[Recovery using Potions]: Amount of PS/PM/RES restored depends on the potion consumed.
However, potions have a cooldown before they can be re-used.
{memo }{nl}{nl}[Destroying Raíces Cristal del Árbol]: Destroying a Raíz Cristal del Árbol will restore the Resistencia of all nearby players.
Destroying a Raíz Cristal del Árbol recovers your Resistencia.
Resistencia of all the players nearby will be restored when you destroy a Raíz Cristal del Árbol.
Liga de Batalla en Equipo is a 5:5 team battle among players.
If Party and all party members press accept, system will search for opponents. When matching opponent party is found, you will move to battle zone to begin the battle.
You need to win two of three matches to win.

is used to warp between Estatua de Diosas when activated.

and does not consume the Pergamino de Teletranporte when you warp back.

Adopt and train companions. They can aid you in combat and transport.
You can adopt a companion by paying the fee required.
{nl}{nl}The companion follows and helps the player in combat and receives EXP therefore.
can ride the companion in combat.
Press {img F9 40 40} to view information of the companion following you.

Companions consume stamina when you bring them along. A companion's movement speed will decrease when there is no stamina. {nl}{nl}Click the switch button to change the companion's status to Modo Descanso.
You can recover a companion's stamina by feeding it food. {nl}{nl}Its PS will be fully recovered and stamina will be partially recovered.
Companion food can be purchased from the Companion Trader PNJ.
Train your companion through the Companion Trader to increase its abilities. A training fee is required.

Add Magic Amulet on weapons and shields for additional effects.
After {img mouseclick_left 40 40} Magic Amulet, when you {img mouseclick_right 40 40} the equipment, a magic amulet will be attached to the equipment.
Potential is consumed when you attach a Magic Amulet.
You can check the attached amulet from the tooltip of the item.
You can't eliminate the attached magic amulet unlike a gem and can't enhance it.
When you are equipped with the equipment with a magic amulet attached, you can see the magic amulet swaying from the equipment.
Exterminio will be activated if you inflict more damages with a powerful attack to a monstruo than its remaining PS.
You can engage in a 1:1 Card Battle with another player using Monster Cards.
When you defeat a Boss Monster, it is possible to obtain its Monster Card.
When you input, Card Battle Table will be opened.{nl}Your opponent can participate in a Card Battle by pressing {img SPACE 40 40}.
You will be ready for the Card Battle once you have selected a card from your inventory.{nl}The selected card will be shown as undisclosed to your opponent.
When both players have decided on their cards, they'll disclose their cards and the win/loss will be decided using the Roulette.
The win/loss will be decided by comparing the monstruos' number of legs, height, weight, number of stars, etc.
The winner and loser will be decided based on the information on the card.
The winner will obtain the loser's card.
You can use the obtained card as material to enhance the other card you have which will increase the number of stars.
By pressing {img Insert 40 40}, you can go into Modo Descanso to use it.

Lapemiter is a unique occupation that is highly respected, but is also looked down upon among Lapes. A Lapemiter serves a religious role, but the other Lapes don't put great emphasis on religious rituals, so they want a Lapemiter to do their exhausting duty.

Unlike the prejudice of the humans, Lapezards are not Lapes that obtained their current status through long training. Most of them are selected by their breeds and they grow up accordingly and receive the necessary food to become a Lapezard.
Their status is not high among Lapes, but they are most dangerous and they get encountered often. To receive respect from the other Lapes, they act violently to the ones they encounter with.
For a Lape to Lapflammer, they just need to obtain the weapons they need. But its not that easy since when Lapflammers die, the weapons also get destroyed so its not that easy for the Lapes.

Ferret Arqueros usually engages in battles, but they sometimes shoot down the fruits on tall trees. It's not that other ferrets asked them to do it, but they just do that for fun when they are not engaged in battles.
They sometimes move the objects, but they usually share the processed fruit products to other ferrets. It is unknown whether they receive any rewards for that or they are responsible to do so.
They look small, but they are matured ferrets. They sometimes become other ferrets depending on the properties of the breeds and the environment that they live in.
This ferret does not possess any distinct characteristic. But due to long labor, they possess strong power, so you should not underestimate it.
They do work while supervising the works of other ferrets.
This ferret is responsible for looking for other enemies and useful fruits.
Like Ferret Arqueros, they either attack enemies or shoot down the fruits. One advantage they have over Arqueros is that they sometimes use hard fruits as bullets.
This ferret has an inferior status compared to the other ferrets. This ferret helps with the works of other ferrets and they also participate in battles.
It is not assured that the Lapeman is the undead of a Lape. However, the Lapeman mostly receives respect from the other Lapes.

With Resurrection, you are able to resurrect your character that has become incapaz de combatir.

There are different options on how to resurrect.{nl} {nl}- Respawn from nearest Revival Point : Revive in the starting location of the map. For dungeons, you will revive outside its entrance.{nl} {nl}- Resurrect using Cristal del Almas : Your character will resurrect at the exact location where it became incapaz de combatir. Using this option, 1 Soul Cristal will be used up from your inventory.
{nl} {nl}When you become incapaz de combatir in dungeons, the gems you possess from your inventory will be dropped to the ground.

{nl} {nl}When you fail enhancing weapons +5 or higher, the potential will be depleted and the enhancement effect will also be reduced by 1. When the potential falls below 0, the item will be destroyed.
Materials for gem enhancement are other gems, Monster Gems and gem abrasives.
When extracting gems, its level can reduce by 1 and Monster Gems or gems that are level 1 or below can be destroyed.
{nl} {nl}Monster Gems can be obtained with a certain probability from hunting monstruos.
Monster Gems have an effect of increasing certain skill levels when they are equipped onto equipment.
However, Monster Gems cannot be enhanced and it may get destroyed when trying to extract it, so be careful.
{nl} {nl}The effects of subweapons will be exerted when you use subweapons with special features.
Items that you've obtained during your adventure can be sold through the Market.

Pergaminos de Teletranporte can be purchased from the TP Shop and enables you to warp without a Estatua de Diosa nearby you.
However, you can only warp to areas where you've activated the Estatua de Diosa.

Only the Templario class is able to create a guild.
A Templario character is able to create a guild by paying a fee to Knight Commander Uska.
You can invite characters to the guild by pressing {img mouseclick_right 40 40} on a character.
The líder del clan is able to build a Guild Tower in a field.
The features of a Guild Tower can be diversified depending on the Templario's Guild Tower skill.
Guild members are able to use the various features such as Warp or Storage from the Guild Tower.
You can upgrade the level of a guild by donating to the Guild Tower.
When a guild level is increased, you will obtain points. Using points, you can upgrade the guild attributes of the guild.
The Escondite de Clan becomes available when the level of your Guild Tower is high enough.
The Escondite de Clan becomes available when the skill level of the líder del clan's Guild Tower is high enough.
In the Escondite de Clan, you are able to harvest crops.
Or you can parcel the baby companion by keeping the baby.
Crops and companions can be obtained through various guild events.
Guild members are able to participate in guild events.
The líder del clan is able to select a guild event from the Guild Tower.
Available guild events such as boss raids and guild competition events will be prepared.
You can obtain companions and crops through the Escondite de Clan.
Guilds are able to fight with each other through a war.
A guild can declare war against another guild.
The guild that is at war can destroy the enemy's Guild Tower and face their enemies in fields. (PvP)

Shinobis are warriors who are familiar with special tactics called Ninjutsu. Only few can overcome the long and harsh training required to become a Shinobi.
Dragóns are elite warriors who are specialized in using spears for battle. They benefit from using two-handed spears.
Templarios are commanding leaders who organize guilds and lead those within their guild. Only a Templario can become a líder del clan and determine the outcome of his or her guild.
Criomantes use powerful ice magic to freeze enemies, or protect their allies from enemies by using ice walls.
Vinculadors link allies together to reduce incoming damage, or connect enemies to amplify the inflicted damage.
Brujos are wizards who harness the power of evil spirits. They can summon evil spirits and can command them to defeat monstruos.
Chamáns are wizards who utilize the power of incantations. They can absorb an enemy's life, or help allies by making enemies weak from a curse.
Rune Casters are wizards who use ancient symbols imbued with magic. Although it takes some time to draw energy from the symbols, they contain enormous power.
Cañoneros are Arqueros who uses powerful cannons to deal massive damage from above, or blast flying enemies from below.
Mosqueteros are equipped with rifles. Even though they cannot use a bow at the same time, they have effective skills for continuous hits and close combat techniques.
Escultor Santo can carve and place sacred statues. Their statues can protect allies or attack enemies.
The Capellán is an army based class that uses divine power to aid allies in combat. Only advanced Sacerdotes at a high level can become a Capellán.
Médico de Plagass are Sacerdotes who can heal the status ailments of allies, or incinerate an enemy with a status ailment. Their special Bird Beak Mask has a special drug to block status ailments.
Cabalistas are Sacerdotes who practice an ancient magic known as Kabbalah. They can support allies by using infinite power, or attack by using a defense formation to disintegrate the enemy's name.

The soldiers searching for the missing residents of Cobalt Forest reported the appearance of a Poata. Derrota the Poata to allow the soldiers to search for the missing people of Cobalt Forest in safety.
The historians investigating the Akmens Ridge reported a Kirmeleech attack. Derrota the Kirmeleech to allow the historians to investigate the Akmens Ridge in safety.
A group of treasure Cazadors climbed up the steep Meseta del Rey in search of the treasures of the stonemason family and are asking for help. Derrota the Giant Goblin de Madera threatening them.
Baron Allerno's reckless greed has the entire barony taken over by evil energy, which is now attracting a Bebraspion. Derrota the Bebraspion for the safety of the barony residents.
Baron Allerno deployed all of his soldiers to experiments, helping a Rocktortuga enter an unguarded area of Tenants' Farm. Derrota the Rocktortuga for the safety of Tentants' Farm.

The Secoya was created to protect the Esculturas de Búho, but recently it became uncontrollable and corrupted by evil energy. If the Esculturas de Búho are destroyed, not a single soul will be able to return to the Diosa. Derrota the Secoya and protect the Esculturas de Búho.
The Salamander is becoming stronger with the power of Señor Demonio Marnox's cursed idol. Derrota the Salamander before it becomes too powerful.

A powerful monstruo named Iltiswort ha aparecido in Dadan Forest due to the aftermath of the demons' plan involving the Kruvina. Derrota the Iltiswort for the safety of the herbalists and the people of the Croa Village.
A powerful monstruo named Guante Demoníaco is keeping people from chasing away the demons in the Novaha Monasterio. Derrota the Deviglove to restore peace in the monastery.
The Colimencia in the Absenta Reservoir is drinking the red water and becoming more powerful. Derrota it before it's too late.
With all its residents missing, the Delmore Castle was invaded by a Denóptico. Derrota it and help Mage Melchioras destroy the remnants of the Kruvina experiment in Delmore Castle.
There are rumors of a Mothstem appearing among the peregrinos passing by the Galeed Plateau. Keep the peregrinos safe by defeating the Mothstem.

The evil energy gathered at Bosque Kateen is attracting all sorts of dangerous monstruos. The Blue Woodspirit in Saknis Plains is particularly threatening to the soldiers stationed there. Derrota the Blue Woodspirit and protect the soldiers.
The demons invading the Torre del Mago are building up their forces. Derrota the Fire Lord that's occupying Torre del Mago 2P to demoralize the demons.

The Escultor Santo Master received a letter from Tesla.{nl}Tesla created several Spirit Guide Esculturas de Búho and the Secoya to protect them. However, the Secoya was corrupted by the demons' evil energy and is destroying the statues and setting fire to the forest. Tesla is now looking for a brave adventurer to defeat the Secoya.

A letter arrived from Historiador Cyrenia Odell.{nl}The demons have secretly invaded the church that was destroyed to keep the secret of the Mausoleo Real of the Great King Zachariel after its construction. Cyrenia is now looking for someone to stop the demons before they can build up their forces.

Ha llegado un mensaje de la Diosa Vakarine.{nl}Luego de que los Reveladores castigaran a los Señores Demonios en la Prisión Demoníaca, sus segundos al mando está reuniendo tropas para ver quien los sucederá. La Diosa Vakarine y los Kupoles aún no lográn recuperarse por completo luego de los eventos recientes y buscan un Revelador que los ayude a detener a los demonios.
